/* -*- C++ -*- */

/** @namespace rapidxml
 * @brief Rapid XML library
 *
 * This distribution of TREX embeds the rapidxml library
 * (http://rapidxml.sourceforge.net/) which is used for parsing
 * TREX configurations files. This namespace is embeds all the
 * utiliies provided by this library.
 *
 * If one prefer to use a different version of  this file it can
 * either define the @c RAPID_XML variable on its shell to point
 * where the headers are located. For example in bash :
 * @code
 * export RAPID_XML=/usr/local/include/rapidxml
 * @endcode
 * Alternatively he can changes the definition of this variable in
 * the @c PlatformRules file
 */
